Title:  Sketch Out Your Book's Overall Structure

Seq:    4

Level:  2

Body:

How will your book be structured? 

Before going too far, it's good to consider some elements of traditional book design. 

The [Wikipedia page on this subject](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Book_design#Back_matter_(end_matter)) is a good place to start. 

Along with the structure, consider how you want the various elements of the book to be numbered. 
